<HEADLINE>
<P>
PETE SCHABARUM ON TERM LIMITS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I'm feeling inclined to kid you people and say that for once I'm agreeing with 
you. 
</P>
<P>
That was an insightful section dealing with Prop. 140 (Perspectives on Term 
Limits, Commentary, Nov. 13). Do note that we're Republicans here. 
</P>
<P>
We voters must have just gotten a taste of how frustrating it is to be a 
legislator, in that the things you vote for have predictably both good and bad 
results. Things just can't be simple, no way. 
</P>
<P>
DIANE STILES 
</P>
<P>
Redondo Beach 
</P>
