<P>
BAN THIS RECIPE? 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I would like you to know that I was really offended by a recipe for "Better 
Than Sex Cake" (Culinary SOS, Oct. 11). 
</P>
<P>
The cake sounded good, but I won't try it because each time I did I'd have to 
confront my feeling of distaste. To my mind, giving a cake this name showed a 
lack of fitness and was out of place. Can't sex be kept out of the kitchen? 
It's everywhere else. 
</P>
