Pacific Bank in Vista after an October holdup. A record number of bank 
robberies have taken place in the county this year. ; Photo, The Fanny Pack 
Bandit during an August holdup in San Diego. ; Photo, The Nike Bandit is 
photographed after robbing a Bank of America branch in San Diego. He orders 
bank tellers to "Just do it." 
</P>
