ENGLAND -- GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS; ENGLAND -- ELECTIONS; CONSERVATIVE PARTY 
(ENGLAND); HESELTINE, MICHAEL; HURD, DOUGLAS; MAJOR, JOHN; LEADERSHIP; KINNOCK, 
NEIL 
