<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY FOCUS: COSTA MESA; 
</P>
<P>
OCC SENDS OUT ITS SPRING SCHEDULE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The 1991 spring class schedule for Orange Coast College is available to the 
public. 
</P>
<P>
The 120-page booklet has been mailed to households in the Coast Community 
College District and may also be picked up at the Admissions and Records 
Building. 
</P>
<P>
The schedule includes a list of all 2,500 classes offered at OCC this spring. 
It also contains information on financial aid, enrollment procedures and 
support services. 
</P>
<P>
The spring semester starts Jan. 22. "Late start," 15-week classes begin the 
week of Feb. 11. 
</P>
<P>
Returning students may register by mail and telephone during November. 
Registration by appointment begins Dec. 12 and open registration, on a 
first-come, first-served basis, starts Jan. 17. For more information, call 
(714) 432-5772. 
</P>
</TEXT>
