<P>
LSU TRIMS ITS LIST TO FOUR CANDIDATES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Louisiana State has cut its list of coaching candidates to four -- Dick 
Sheridan of North Carolina State, Bobby Ross of Georgia Tech, Curley Hallman of 
Southern Mississippi and former Pittsburgh coach Mike Gottfried. LSU Coach Mike 
Archer leaves the job after the Tigers' season-ending game Saturday against 
Tulane. 
