fill the "makeup guru" void. Some Orange County clients think he's on his way. 
; Photo, Richard Stevens calls consultations seminars rather than makeovers. 
DON KELSEN / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Tani Wright, left, before session. 
Stevens emphasized her eyes and mouth, right. 
</P>
